<nav class="nav" id="nav" data-screen-label="Nav"><svg class="sunmark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"><circle class="sun-disc" cx="16" cy="16" r="10"></circle></svg><a class="wm" href="/">AMPM <small>BUILDING SERVICES</small></a><div class="links"><a href="/services/" class="">Services</a><a href="/work/" class="">Work</a><a href="/compliance/" class="">Compliance</a><a href="/about/" class="">About</a><a href="/contact/" class="">Contact</a></div><a class="phone" href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></nav><div class="page" style="--svc: var(--m-purple);"><div class="shell"><section class="sec p-hero"><div class="reveal in"><span class="svc-bar" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span></div><div class="reveal in"><div class="kicker">Sectors</div></div><h1 class="reveal d1 in">Residential &amp; BTR</h1><p class="lede reveal d2 in">Apartment blocks and build-to-rent schemes are won and lost on safety, compliance and the resident experience. Under the Building Safety Act, higher-risk buildings need building services that are demonstrably safe, fully evidenced and delivered around the people who live there. We bring MEPH, fit-out, fabric and external works together under one accountable team — so the building hands over safe, compliant and let-ready on a single date.</p><div class="reveal d3 in" style="margin-top: 28px;"><a class="btn line sm" href="/contact/">Enquire about Residential &amp; BTR →</a></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">Across every trade</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Four service lines,<br>under one team.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-green);"></span><span><a href="/meph/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">MEPH</a></span></h4><ul><li>Communal heating, hot water &amp; ventilation</li><li>Landlord power, lighting &amp; life-safety systems</li><li>Water hygiene, tanks &amp; Legionella control</li><li>Data, comms &amp; smart metering for billing</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span><a href="/commercial/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Commercial Fit-out</a></span></h4><ul><li>Amenity &amp; communal spaces — gyms, lounges &amp; co-working</li><li>Lobbies, concierge &amp; resident entrances</li><li>Apartment fit-out, kitchens &amp; bathrooms</li><li>Durable, hard-wearing finishes for high turnover</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span><a href="/fabric/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Fabric</a></span></h4><ul><li>Cladding, recladding &amp; external wall systems</li><li>Building-safety &amp; fire remediation works</li><li>Balconies, windows &amp; curtain walling</li><li>Thermal &amp; fabric upgrades to Part L</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span><a href="/groundworks/" style="color:inherit;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;text-decoration-thickness:2px;">Landscaping</a></span></h4><ul><li>Courtyards, podium decks &amp; roof terraces</li><li>Play areas &amp; shared amenity space</li><li>Resident &amp; visitor parking &amp; surfacing</li><li>Boundaries, gates &amp; secure access</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">What matters</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Built around your<br>building.</h2></div><div class="capgroups reveal in"><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span>Built around residents</span></h4><ul><li>Working in occupied, tenanted blocks without disruption</li><li>Resident liaison, notices &amp; managed access to homes</li><li>Out-of-hours scheduling &amp; strict noise management</li><li>Phased, block-by-block handover and re-let turnaround</li><li>Security, safeguarding &amp; DBS-aware site teams</li></ul></div><div class="capgroup"><h4><span class="dot" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span>Building safety, handled</span></h4><ul><li>Building Safety Act 2022 for higher-risk buildings</li><li>The golden thread — records that follow the building</li><li>BS 8414 / BR 135 for cladding &amp; external wall systems</li><li>CDM 2015 across design and construction</li><li>Building Regs Part B fire safety &amp; BS 7671 electrical</li></ul></div></div></section><section class="sec tight"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 28px;"><div class="kicker">FAQs</div><h2 class="dhead sm">Your questions,<br>answered.</h2></div><div class="faq reveal in"><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you carry out building-safety and cladding remediation?</summary><p>Yes. We deliver cladding replacement, recladding and wider fire-remediation works on apartment blocks and higher-risk buildings, with external wall systems tested to BS 8414 and assessed against BR 135, and full records handed over for the safety case.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Can you work in occupied residential blocks?</summary><p>Yes. Most residential and BTR works are phased around live, tenanted buildings — resident notices, managed access, out-of-hours working and noise control — so people keep living at home while we work. We hand over block by block.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you handle the golden thread and safety case records?</summary><p>Yes. We maintain the golden thread of information required under the Building Safety Act 2022 — as-built drawings, fire-stopping records, certification and O&amp;M data — handed over in a structured set that feeds the building's safety case.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Do you cover communal M&amp;E and water hygiene?</summary><p>Yes. We self-deliver communal heating, ventilation, landlord power and lighting, plus water hygiene — tanks, distribution and Legionella control — with smart metering for resident billing. BS 7671 electrical certification is provided throughout.</p></details><details class="faq-item"><summary>Which areas do you cover?</summary><p>London and the South East, including Sussex, Surrey, Kent, Hampshire and Berkshire.</p></details></div></section><section class="sec tight line-top"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 24px;"><div class="kicker">Our service lines</div><h2 class="dhead sm">One contractor,<br>four service lines.</h2></div><div class="otherlines reveal in"><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-green);"></span><span class="ol-nm">MEPH</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Commercial Fit-out</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Fabric</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div><div class="otherline"><span class="ol-l"><span class="ol-sw" style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span><span class="ol-nm">Landscaping</span></span><span class="ol-go">→</span></div></div></section></div><section class="band" data-nav-dark="true" style="background: var(--m-green); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div class="shell"><div class="cta-split reveal in"><div><div class="kicker on-dark">Talk to us about MEPH</div><h2 class="dhead sm" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">Scope, programme,<br>stage — send it over.</h2><p class="body" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9); margin-top: 16px;">A named contact, not a sales team, comes back within 24 hours. Include the package, programme a